{{Expand Polish|Sobolewski|date=May 2012}} '''Sobolewski''' ({{IPA|sɔbɔˈlɛfskʲi}}) is a [[Polish language|Polish]] [[locational surname]], which means a person from places in Poland called [[Sobolew (disambiguation)|Sobolew]] or [[Sobolewo (disambiguation)|Sobolewo]], both derived from the Polish ''sobol'', meaning "[[sable]]".<ref>''Dictionary of American Family Names''. [http://www.ancestry.com/name-origin?surname=sobolewski "Sobolewski Family History"], Oxford University Press, 2013.</ref>
